data.description: Looking for a beautiful town home in Swan Valley? Look no further. This 3 bedroom/2 1/2 bath town home is nestled in the heart of Swan Valley, Idaho. This 1,735 sqft home is an owners paradise looking for a weekend getaway or for a full time residence. The community within the association regularly meet in the common areas to watch their dogs run about and catch up on daily events. TheSwan Valley General Store, Rainey Creek Center and the Roadhouse Bar & Grill are a short walk over the bridge that straddles RaineyCreek itself. No need to jump in your vehicle here. What brings people to Swan Valley are the many outdoor recreational activities. The South Fork of the Snake River is recognized as the west's premier dry fly river. Palisades Reservoir exists for water skiing, pleasure boating & fishing. There are countless miles of Forest Service trails for the outdoorsman and miles of downhill ski slopes at nearby Targhee and Jackson Hole Ski Resorts.
